trans-unit.source: Represents an association between a source <xref href="System.IO.Packaging.Package"></xref> or <xref href="System.IO.Packaging.PackagePart"></xref>, and a target object which can be a <xref href="System.IO.Packaging.PackagePart"></xref> or external resource.
trans-unit.target: Representerar en association mellan en källa <xref href="System.IO.Packaging.Package"> </xref> eller <xref href="System.IO.Packaging.PackagePart"> </xref>, och ett målobjekt som kan vara en <xref href="System.IO.Packaging.PackagePart"> </xref> eller en extern resurs.

trans-unit.source: A PackageRelationship defines an association between a *source* <xref:System.IO.Packaging.Package> or <xref:System.IO.Packaging.PackagePart> to a *target* <xref:System.IO.Packaging.PackagePart> or external resource.
trans-unit.target: En PackageRelationship definierar en association mellan en *källa* <xref:System.IO.Packaging.Package>eller <xref:System.IO.Packaging.PackagePart>till en *mål* <xref:System.IO.Packaging.PackagePart>eller en extern resurs.</xref:System.IO.Packaging.PackagePart> </xref:System.IO.Packaging.PackagePart> </xref:System.IO.Packaging.Package>

trans-unit.source: The source object is considered the "owner" of the relationship.
trans-unit.target: Källobjektet betraktas som "ägare" för relationen.

trans-unit.source: The PackageRelationship class has no public constructor; instead, two Create methods are used: ||| |-|-| |<xref:System.IO.Packaging.Package>.<xref:System.IO.Packaging.Package.CreateRelationship%2A>|Creates a "package-level" relationship—from a package to a specified part or external resource.| |<xref:System.IO.Packaging.PackagePart>.<xref:System.IO.Packaging.PackagePart.CreateRelationship%2A>|Creates a "part-level" relationship—from one part to another part or external resource.| The source package or part is identified by the <xref:System.IO.Packaging.PackageRelationship.SourceUri%2A> property of the relationship.
trans-unit.target: PackageRelationship-klassen har ingen offentlig konstruktor; i stället två skapa metoder som används: ||| |-|-| | <xref:System.IO.Packaging.Package>. <xref:System.IO.Packaging.Package.CreateRelationship%2A>| Skapar en relation "paketet på objektnivå" – från ett paket till en angiven del eller en extern resurs. | | <xref:System.IO.Packaging.PackagePart>. <xref:System.IO.Packaging.PackagePart.CreateRelationship%2A>| Skapar en relation "del-nivån", från en del till en annan del eller en extern resurs. | Källpaket eller en del identifieras av den <xref:System.IO.Packaging.PackageRelationship.SourceUri%2A>egenskapen i relationen.</xref:System.IO.Packaging.PackageRelationship.SourceUri%2A> </xref:System.IO.Packaging.PackagePart.CreateRelationship%2A> </xref:System.IO.Packaging.PackagePart> </xref:System.IO.Packaging.Package.CreateRelationship%2A> </xref:System.IO.Packaging.Package>

trans-unit.source: The target part or external resource is identified by the <xref:System.IO.Packaging.PackageRelationship.TargetUri%2A> property of the relationship.
trans-unit.target: Den mål eller extern resurs som identifieras av den <xref:System.IO.Packaging.PackageRelationship.TargetUri%2A>egenskapen i relationen.</xref:System.IO.Packaging.PackageRelationship.TargetUri%2A>

trans-unit.source: Creating or deleting a relationship does not affect the source or target objects in any way.
trans-unit.target: Skapa eller ta bort en relation påverkar inte käll- eller objekt på något sätt.

trans-unit.source: If a source object is deleted, all relationships owned by the object are also deleted.
trans-unit.target: Om ett källobjekt tas bort raderas även alla relationer som ägs av objektet.

trans-unit.source: Relationships enable navigation both in a document and between documents.
trans-unit.target: Relationer aktivera navigering både i ett dokument och mellan dokument.

trans-unit.source: Relationships also support document object model services, such as linking a <xref:System.Printing.PrintTicket> to specific document elements when printing.
trans-unit.target: Relationer stöder även dokumentet objektet model-tjänster, till exempel länka en <xref:System.Printing.PrintTicket>till dokumentelement utskrift.</xref:System.Printing.PrintTicket>

trans-unit.source: For more information about PackageRelationship elements see Section 1.3 "Relationships" in the *Open Packaging Conventions* specification available for download at [http://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?LinkID=71255](http://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?LinkID=71255).
trans-unit.target: Mer information om PackageRelationship element finns i avsnittet 1.3 "Relationer" i den *Open Packaging Conventions* specifikation som är tillgänglig för hämtning på [http://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?LinkID=71255](http://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?LinkID=71255).

trans-unit.source: Gets a string that identifies the relationship.
trans-unit.target: Hämtar en sträng som identifierar relationen.

trans-unit.source: The Id property string is unique for all relationships owned by the <xref:System.IO.Packaging.PackageRelationship.SourceUri%2A> package or part.
trans-unit.target: Egenskapen Id-strängen är unikt för alla relationer som ägs av <xref:System.IO.Packaging.PackageRelationship.SourceUri%2A>paket eller skulle hämtas.</xref:System.IO.Packaging.PackageRelationship.SourceUri%2A>

trans-unit.source: The Id is specified in the call to the **Package**.<xref:System.IO.Packaging.Package.CreateRelationship%2A> or **PackagePart**.<xref:System.IO.Packaging.PackagePart.CreateRelationship%2A> method that created the relationship.
trans-unit.target: Id som har angetts i anropet till den **paketet**.<xref:System.IO.Packaging.Package.CreateRelationship%2A> eller **PackagePart**.<xref:System.IO.Packaging.PackagePart.CreateRelationship%2A> metod som skapade relationen.</xref:System.IO.Packaging.PackagePart.CreateRelationship%2A> </xref:System.IO.Packaging.Package.CreateRelationship%2A>

trans-unit.source: After the relationship is created, the Id cannot be changed.
trans-unit.target: När du har skapat relationen kan inte Id ändras.

trans-unit.source: The Id property string is a valid XML identifier.
trans-unit.target: Egenskapen Id-strängen är en giltig XML-identifierare.

trans-unit.source: The Id type is xsd:ID and must follow the naming conventions prescribed in the *XML Schema Part 2: Datatypes* specification (see [http://www.w3.org/TR/xmlschema-2/#ID](http://www.w3.org/TR/xmlschema-2/)).
trans-unit.target: Typ-Id är xsd: ID och måste följa namnkonventionerna föreskrivs i den *XML Schema del 2: datatyper* specifikationen (se [http://www.w3.org/TR/xmlschema-2/#ID](http://www.w3.org/TR/xmlschema-2/)).

trans-unit.source: A string that identifies the relationship.
trans-unit.target: En sträng som identifierar relationen.

trans-unit.source: Gets the <xref href="System.IO.Packaging.Package"></xref> that contains this relationship.
trans-unit.target: Hämtar den <xref href="System.IO.Packaging.Package"> </xref> som innehåller den här relationen.

trans-unit.source: For more information about <xref:System.IO.Packaging.Package> elements see the *Open Packaging Conventions* specification available for download at [http://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?LinkID=71255](http://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?LinkID=71255).
trans-unit.target: Mer information om <xref:System.IO.Packaging.Package>elementen finns i *Open Packaging Conventions* specifikation som är tillgänglig för hämtning på [http://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?LinkID=71255](http://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?LinkID=71255).</xref:System.IO.Packaging.Package>

trans-unit.source: The package that contains this relationship.
trans-unit.target: Det paket som innehåller den här relationen.

trans-unit.source: Gets the qualified type name of the relationship.
trans-unit.target: Hämtar det kvalificerade typnamnet för relationen.

trans-unit.source: The RelationshipType is specified in the call to the **Package**.<xref:System.IO.Packaging.Package.CreateRelationship%2A> or **PackagePart**.<xref:System.IO.Packaging.PackagePart.CreateRelationship%2A> method that created the relationship.
trans-unit.target: RelationshipType har angetts i anropet till den **paketet**.<xref:System.IO.Packaging.Package.CreateRelationship%2A> eller **PackagePart**.<xref:System.IO.Packaging.PackagePart.CreateRelationship%2A> metod som skapade relationen.</xref:System.IO.Packaging.PackagePart.CreateRelationship%2A> </xref:System.IO.Packaging.Package.CreateRelationship%2A>

trans-unit.source: After the relationship is created, the RelationshipType cannot be changed.
trans-unit.target: När du har skapat relationen kan inte RelationshipType ändras.

trans-unit.source: RelationshipType is defined in a URI-like syntax and identifies the role of the relationship.
trans-unit.target: RelationshipType är definierad i en URI-liknande syntax och identifierar rollen för relationen.

trans-unit.source: For example, "http://schemas.microsoft.com/xps/2005/06/required-resource" identifies the relationship to a target part that is a "required-resource."
trans-unit.target: Till exempel identifierar "http://schemas.microsoft.com/xps/2005/06/required-resource" förhållandet mellan en del av mål som är en "required-resource."

trans-unit.source: **Package-Wide Relationship Types** |Description|Relationship Type| |-----------------|-----------------------| |Core Properties|http://schemas.microsoft.com/package/2006/relationships/metadata/core-properties| |Digital Signature|http://schemas.microsoft.com/package/2006/relationships/digital-signature/signature| |Digital Signature Certificate|http://schemas.microsoft.com/package/2006/relationships/digital-signature/certificate| |Digital Signature Origin|http://schemas.microsoft.com/package/2006/relationships/digital-signature/origin| |Thumbnail|http://schemas.microsoft.com/package/2006/relationships/metadata/thumbnail| For more information about package relationship types see Chapter 3 and Appendix I of the *Open Packaging Conventions* specification available for download at [http://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?LinkID=71255](http://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?LinkID=71255).
trans-unit.target: **Paketet hela relationstyper** | Beskrivning | Relationstypen | |-----------------|-----------------------| | Viktiga egenskaper | http://schemas.microsoft.com/package/2006/relationships/metadata/core-properties | | Digital signatur | http://schemas.microsoft.com/package/2006/relationships/digital-signature/signature | | Digital Signaturcertifikat | http://schemas.microsoft.com/package/2006/relationships/digital-signature/certificate | | Digital Signature Origin | http://schemas.microsoft.com/package/2006/relationships/digital-signature/origin | | Miniatyr | http://schemas.microsoft.com/package/2006/relationships/metadata/thumbnail | Mer information om paketet relation typer finns kapitel 3 och tillägg I i den *Open Packaging Conventions* specifikation som är tillgänglig för hämtning på [http://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?LinkID=71255](http://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?LinkID=71255).

trans-unit.source: The qualified type name of the relationship.
trans-unit.target: Kvalificerat typnamn för relationen.

trans-unit.source: Gets the [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_uri](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-uri-md.md)] of the package or part that owns the relationship.
trans-unit.target: Hämtar den [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_uri](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-uri-md.md)] på paketet eller en del som äger relationen.

trans-unit.source: If the relationship is owned by a <xref:System.IO.Packaging.Package>, SourceUri returns a URI of "/".
trans-unit.target: Om relationen ägs av en <xref:System.IO.Packaging.Package>, SourceUri returnerar en URI för "/".</xref:System.IO.Packaging.Package>

trans-unit.source: If the relationship is owned by a <xref:System.IO.Packaging.PackagePart>, SourceUri returns the URI of the part.
trans-unit.target: Om relationen ägs av en <xref:System.IO.Packaging.PackagePart>SourceUri Returnerar URI för skulle hämtas.</xref:System.IO.Packaging.PackagePart>

trans-unit.source: The [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_uri](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-uri-md.md)] of the <xref href="System.IO.Packaging.Package"></xref> or <xref href="System.IO.Packaging.PackagePart"></xref> that owns the relationship.
trans-unit.target: Den [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_uri](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-uri-md.md)] av den <xref href="System.IO.Packaging.Package"> </xref> eller <xref href="System.IO.Packaging.PackagePart"> </xref> som äger relationen.

trans-unit.source: Gets a value that indicates whether the target of the relationship is <xref href="System.IO.Packaging.TargetMode"></xref> or <xref href="System.IO.Packaging.TargetMode"></xref> to the <xref href="System.IO.Packaging.Package"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Hämtar ett värde som anger om målet för relationen är <xref href="System.IO.Packaging.TargetMode"> </xref> eller <xref href="System.IO.Packaging.TargetMode"> </xref> till den <xref href="System.IO.Packaging.Package"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: The TargetMode is specified in the call to the **Package**.<xref:System.IO.Packaging.Package.CreateRelationship%2A> or **PackagePart**.<xref:System.IO.Packaging.PackagePart.CreateRelationship%2A> method that created the relationship.
trans-unit.target: TargetMode har angetts i anropet till den **paketet**.<xref:System.IO.Packaging.Package.CreateRelationship%2A> eller **PackagePart**.<xref:System.IO.Packaging.PackagePart.CreateRelationship%2A> metod som skapade relationen.</xref:System.IO.Packaging.PackagePart.CreateRelationship%2A> </xref:System.IO.Packaging.Package.CreateRelationship%2A>

trans-unit.source: After the relationship is created the TargetMode cannot be changed.
trans-unit.target: När relationen skapas kan inte TargetMode ändras.

trans-unit.source: When TargetMode is <xref:System.IO.Packaging.TargetMode>, the <xref:System.IO.Packaging.PackageRelationship.TargetUri%2A> MUST be a relative reference.
trans-unit.target: När TargetMode är <xref:System.IO.Packaging.TargetMode>, <xref:System.IO.Packaging.PackageRelationship.TargetUri%2A>måste vara en relativ referens.</xref:System.IO.Packaging.PackageRelationship.TargetUri%2A> </xref:System.IO.Packaging.TargetMode>

trans-unit.source: For a package-level relationship, the relative reference of the <xref:System.IO.Packaging.PackageRelationship.TargetUri%2A> is resolved relative to the pack URI of the source package that owns and contains the relationship.
trans-unit.target: För en paket-nivå relation relativa referera av den <xref:System.IO.Packaging.PackageRelationship.TargetUri%2A>löses i förhållande till paket-URI för källpaket som äger och innehåller relationen.</xref:System.IO.Packaging.PackageRelationship.TargetUri%2A>

trans-unit.source: (Example source package pack URI: "pack://http:,,www.adatum.com,files,datapak.package/".) For a part-level relationship, the <xref:System.IO.Packaging.PackageRelationship.TargetUri%2A> is resolved relative to the source part that owns the relationship (<xref:System.IO.Packaging.PackageRelationship.TargetUri%2A> is interpreted relative to <xref:System.IO.Packaging.PackageRelationship.SourceUri%2A>).
trans-unit.target: (Exempel källa paketet pack URI: "pack://http:,, www.adatum.com, files,datapak.package/".) För en del nivå relation i <xref:System.IO.Packaging.PackageRelationship.TargetUri%2A>löses i förhållande till källans del som äger relationen (<xref:System.IO.Packaging.PackageRelationship.TargetUri%2A> tolkas förhållande till <xref:System.IO.Packaging.PackageRelationship.SourceUri%2A>).</xref:System.IO.Packaging.PackageRelationship.SourceUri%2A> </xref:System.IO.Packaging.PackageRelationship.TargetUri%2A> </xref:System.IO.Packaging.PackageRelationship.TargetUri%2A>

trans-unit.source: When TargetMode is <xref:System.IO.Packaging.TargetMode>, the <xref:System.IO.Packaging.PackageRelationship.TargetUri%2A> can be either a relative reference or a fully qualified URI.
trans-unit.target: När TargetMode är <xref:System.IO.Packaging.TargetMode>, <xref:System.IO.Packaging.PackageRelationship.TargetUri%2A>kan vara en relativ referens eller en fullständigt kvalificerade URI.</xref:System.IO.Packaging.PackageRelationship.TargetUri%2A> </xref:System.IO.Packaging.TargetMode>

trans-unit.source: If the <xref:System.IO.Packaging.PackageRelationship.TargetUri%2A> is a relative reference, the reference is interpreted as relative to the location of the <xref:System.IO.Packaging.Package> that contains this relationship.
trans-unit.target: Om den <xref:System.IO.Packaging.PackageRelationship.TargetUri%2A>är en relativ referens referensen tolkas som i förhållande till platsen för den <xref:System.IO.Packaging.Package>som innehåller den här relationen.</xref:System.IO.Packaging.Package> </xref:System.IO.Packaging.PackageRelationship.TargetUri%2A>

trans-unit.source: For more information about TargetMode see Section 1.3.3 "Relationship Markup" of the *Open Packaging Conventions* specification available for download at [http://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?LinkID=71255](http://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?LinkID=71255).
trans-unit.target: Mer information om TargetMode i avsnittet 1.3.3 "Relationen Markup" för den *Open Packaging Conventions* specifikation som är tillgänglig för hämtning på [http://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?LinkID=71255](http://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?LinkID=71255).

trans-unit.source: An enumeration value that indicates whether <xref:System.IO.Packaging.PackageRelationship.TargetUri*> references a resource <xref href="System.IO.Packaging.TargetMode"></xref> or <xref href="System.IO.Packaging.TargetMode"></xref> to the <xref href="System.IO.Packaging.Package"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Ett uppräkningsvärde som anger om <xref:System.IO.Packaging.PackageRelationship.TargetUri*>refererar till en resurs <xref href="System.IO.Packaging.TargetMode"> </xref> eller <xref href="System.IO.Packaging.TargetMode"> </xref> till den <xref href="System.IO.Packaging.Package"> </xref>.</xref:System.IO.Packaging.PackageRelationship.TargetUri*>

trans-unit.source: Gets the [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_uri](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-uri-md.md)] of the target resource of the relationship.
trans-unit.target: Hämtar den [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_uri](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-uri-md.md)] för målresursen för relationen.

trans-unit.source: The TargetUri is specified in the call to the **Package**.<xref:System.IO.Packaging.Package.CreateRelationship%2A> or **PackagePart**.<xref:System.IO.Packaging.PackagePart.CreateRelationship%2A> method that created the relationship.
trans-unit.target: TargetUri har angetts i anropet till den **paketet**.<xref:System.IO.Packaging.Package.CreateRelationship%2A> eller **PackagePart**.<xref:System.IO.Packaging.PackagePart.CreateRelationship%2A> metod som skapade relationen.</xref:System.IO.Packaging.PackagePart.CreateRelationship%2A> </xref:System.IO.Packaging.Package.CreateRelationship%2A>

trans-unit.source: After the relationship is created the TargetUri cannot be changed.
trans-unit.target: När relationen skapas kan inte på mål-URI ändras.

trans-unit.source: When <xref:System.IO.Packaging.PackageRelationship.TargetMode%2A> is <xref:System.IO.Packaging.TargetMode>, the TargetUri MUST be a relative reference.
trans-unit.target: När <xref:System.IO.Packaging.PackageRelationship.TargetMode%2A>är <xref:System.IO.Packaging.TargetMode>, mål-URI måste vara en relativ referens.</xref:System.IO.Packaging.TargetMode> </xref:System.IO.Packaging.PackageRelationship.TargetMode%2A>

trans-unit.source: For a package-level relationship, the relative reference of the TargetUri is resolved relative to the pack URI of the source package that owns and contains the relationship.
trans-unit.target: Relativa referensen till TargetUri har lösts i förhållande till paket-URI för källpaket som äger och innehåller relationen för en paket-nivå-relation.

trans-unit.source: (Example source package pack URI: "pack://http:,,www.adatum.com,files,datapak.package/".) For a part-level relationship, the TargetUri is resolved relative to the source part that owns the relationship (TargetUri is interpreted relative to <xref:System.IO.Packaging.PackageRelationship.SourceUri%2A>).
trans-unit.target: (Exempel källa paketet pack URI: "pack://http:,, www.adatum.com, files,datapak.package/".) För en del nivå relation i TargetUri löses i förhållande till källans del som äger relationen (TargetUri tolkas förhållande till <xref:System.IO.Packaging.PackageRelationship.SourceUri%2A>).</xref:System.IO.Packaging.PackageRelationship.SourceUri%2A>

trans-unit.source: When <xref:System.IO.Packaging.PackageRelationship.TargetMode%2A> is <xref:System.IO.Packaging.TargetMode>, the TargetUri can be either a relative reference or a fully qualified URI.
trans-unit.target: När <xref:System.IO.Packaging.PackageRelationship.TargetMode%2A>är <xref:System.IO.Packaging.TargetMode>, TargetUri kan vara en relativ referens eller en fullständigt kvalificerade URI.</xref:System.IO.Packaging.TargetMode> </xref:System.IO.Packaging.PackageRelationship.TargetMode%2A>

trans-unit.source: If the TargetUri is a relative reference, the reference is interpreted as relative to the location of the <xref:System.IO.Packaging.Package> that contains this relationship.
trans-unit.target: Om TargetUri är en relativ referens, referensen tolkas som i förhållande till platsen för den <xref:System.IO.Packaging.Package>som innehåller den här relationen.</xref:System.IO.Packaging.Package>

trans-unit.source: For more information about TargetUri see Section 1.3.3 "Relationship Markup" of the *Open Packaging Conventions* specification available for download at [http://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?LinkID=71255](http://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?LinkID=71255).
trans-unit.target: Mer information om TargetUri i avsnittet 1.3.3 "Relationen Markup" för den *Open Packaging Conventions* specifikation som är tillgänglig för hämtning på [http://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?LinkID=71255](http://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?LinkID=71255).

trans-unit.source: The [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_uri](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-uri-md.md)] of the target resource.
trans-unit.target: Den [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_uri](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-uri-md.md)] för målresursen.
